               <p>I am servant to Mr. Hilbert, who is a <rs id="t17760417-48-viclabel266" type="occupation">mealman</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17760417-48-victim427 t17760417-48-viclabel266"></join>: I sent by the prisoner sixteen quarters of pollard to Mr. Evans, and I sent a note with it, and eight quarters to one Mr. Sharrard.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17760417-48-person430">
