             sworn.</p>
               <p>I counted the sacks when he had shot the pollard, and found two quarter and two bushels short of the quantity.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>My master said if I told the truth he would not hurt a hair of my head.</p>
               <p>EVANS. I did not say any such thing.</p>
               <p>
